description: Little Piece Of Heaven is a mobile eatery roaming the streets of Washington DC. Featuring "Food you can eat every day," their menu includes everything from Hot Dogs, Burgers, Waffles and Wings to Fried Fish and Turkey Legs and Philly Cheese Steaks. Chef Ty mixes it up with daily specials ranging from Mac N' Cheese to Grilled Pork Chops, truly providing something for everyone.
name: Little Piece Of Heaven
